        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "When using the JsonStrategy to render your views and an Exception is thrown, the Exceptions' message is not visible as json_encode is unable to encode the Exception object injected into the view.\r\n\r\nSuggestions would be to either allow assignment of a custom ExceptionStrategy via the ServiceManager, or injecting the exceptions message itself into the returned ViewModel (see line 162 of ExceptionStrategy.php).\r\n\r\nThere doesn't appear to be a way to override the default exception strategy"
        },
